| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0765 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 64be19db-3a1b-56e2-9a8c-9ecc44b61bdd"
